{"lastModified":null,"uri":"c::18121026674::vessel::266426e0-da97-11f0-90ba-894d3ae49d9a","yachtType":["Power Catamaran","Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Cannigione, Sardinia\n\nSailing through the crystal-clear waters of northern Sardinia is nothing short of magical aboard a Aquila 32 Sport. This 2025 motor catamaran embodies the perfect balance of comfort, style, and high performance, making it the ideal companion for those dreaming of waterborne adventures without compromising on luxury.\n\nDesigned with an extended waterline, the Aquila 32 Sport offers a smooth, stable ride, paired with spacious layouts both above and below deck. Every feature has been thoughtfully crafted for maximum onboard enjoyment—from the fixed swim platform, equipped with a cleverly stowed, easy-access ladder, to the air-conditioned cabin, ideal for peaceful nights lulled by the rhythm of the sea.\n\nThe Aquila 32 Sport is more than just a boat; it’s an invitation to explore new horizons. Glide along Sardinia’s breathtaking coastline, discover secluded coves, dock at charming harbors to sample local cuisine, or lose yourself in the tranquil silence of remote islands. Onboard, every moment feels extraordinary—whether basking in the sun with family during the day or sharing laughter with friends under a canopy of stars.\n\nWith its sleek design, outstanding safety features, and effortless handling, this catamaran is a true gem for anyone who dreams of experiencing the sea with complete freedom. The Aquila 32 Sport isn’t just a vessel; it’s a space where lasting memories are created.\n\nor those ready to be captivated by the Mediterranean’s beauty, this catamaran is more than a choice—it’s a gateway to unforgettable experiences. Available for charter in Cannigione, it’s the perfect way to turn your dream voyage into a reality.\n\nBoat available for daily rental in Sardinia.","blueprint":{"name":"AQUILA 32 SPORT","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::266426e0-da97-11f0-90ba-894d3a